2124.subject: MIT
2124.descrlong: A capstone contributes to the disciplines or the professions by adding to technical/professional knowledge or by providing an original application of technical/professional knowledge in the professional field.  Examples include a field study, a project, applied research, or a professional article of publishable quality.  (Credit/No Credit Available)
